resources.string: The Ola Electric has raised curtain from Ola Electric S1 scooter in India with an introductory price of Rs 99,999. The all-new electric scooter is equipped with a 3KWh electric motor and has a range of up to 141 km. With the sports mode, the scooter will run up to 90 km on a single charge.
